title: Interact
body:
OldMan: When I was younger, there weren't any clinics around. Im [c_red]purposely[/c] creating a lot of text to test out the pages feature of Scribbles. Cool!
OldMan: I'm sure glad Dr. Doctor moved down to this small town.
 [[Younger|When I was Young]]

title: When I was Young
body:
OldMan: When I was your age, I had to walk to school up hill both ways
OldMan: Times are different now, y'all have it easy.

title: Tending the Farm
body:
OldMan: I wake up everyday at the brink of dawn to tend to my tomato farm.
OldMan: I don't get paid much, but its honest work.
